tool_description:
Billboard charts API: Weekly Billboard Hot 100, Weekly Billboard 200, Weekly Artist 100, Weekly Billboard Weekly Global 200, Weekly Catalog Albums, Weekly Independent Albums, Weekly Billboard U.S. Afrobeats Songs. Year End Hot 100 Songs, Year End Billboard 200 Albums, Year End Billboard  Global 200, Year End Top Artists, Year End Top Artists – Duo/Group, Year End Top Labels, Year End Top New Artists, Year End Top Artists – Male, Year End Top Artists – Female. 
All Greatest of All Time Charts....

api_list.name: Greatest of All Time Mainstream Rock Artists
api_list.description:
Greatest of All Time Mainstream Rock Artists chart.
See response example
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://billboard-api5.p.rapidapi.com/api/charts/all-time/greatest-of-all-time-mainstream-rock-artists"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "billboard-api5.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
